how to install cassandra in windows:
Download latest MSI file from: https://academy.datastax.com/planet-cassandra/cassandra

if 32 bit windows: make sure Visual C++ 2008 runtime is available

install Java 8
 
<%cassandra Home%>\DataStax-DDC\apache-cassandra\bin cassandra -f
 
add <%cassandra Home%>\DataStax-DDC\apache-cassandra\bin to PATH environmental variable 
 
Open new cmd prompt. run cqlsh
